caillou 's holiday movie is a 2003 canadian direct-to-video animated christmas film directed by nick rijgersberg . the film is based on the canadian tv series caillou . it was released on vhs and dvd in october 7 , 2003 . it was re-released by ncircle entertainment as part of caillou 's 25th anniversary on november 11 , 2014 . this is the first time that caillou is voiced by annie bovaird , who would later voice him in the rest of the tv series ' run . bovaird replaced original voice actress jaclyn linetsky , who died in a car crash a month before the film 's release . it is the only film based on the tv series .